long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Transform your start page into something beautiful with Startify—a fresh way to begin browsing the internet. Choose from a selection of ready-made animated backgrounds, or upload your own for a more personalized experience.

Startify offers a variety of search engines with convenient suggestions, including.

Quick Links let you access your favorite websites instantly, making browsing faster and easier. Customize your start page to keep everything you need within reach.

For more information and support, visit our GitHub: https://github.com/PawelGawlikDev/startify.

Privacy First: Startify is designed with your privacy in mind. We don’t collect any data—no settings, history, or usage data. All settings and files are stored locally on your device.
